title: NFL Playoff Hunt, Rookie QBs, Seahawks-Vikings Recap (Football 12/11)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to break down the biggest storylines from Week 14, including the Chiefs chances of making a deep run and Patrick Mahomes no-look pass (1:30), concerns over the Patriots and whether Tom Brady/Rob Gronkowski are at the end of their run (10:00), if the Steelers are melting down (16:30), ranking AFC contenders (22:15), why Josh Allen might be the best rookie quarterback (27:00), and Kyler Murray's future (34:00). Then the guys break down the Vikings-Seahawks Monday Night Football game (39:50)
